<h1 style="font-size:20px; line-height:22px; height:22px; margin-bottom:10px;">国风·郑风·有女同车</h1>
<p class="source"><a href="https://www.gushiwen.org/shiwen/default.aspx?cstr=%e5%85%88%e7%a7%a6">先秦</a><span>：</span><a href="/search.aspx?value=%e4%bd%9a%e5%90%8d">佚名</a> </p>
<div class="contson" id="contson105d08a95e7d">
<p>有女同车，颜如舜华。将翱将翔，佩玉琼琚。彼美孟姜，洵美且都。<br />有女同行，颜如舜英。将翱将翔，佩玉将将。彼美孟姜，德音不忘。</p>
</div>
</div>
