<p><a style="font-size:18px; line-height:22px; height:22px;" href="/shiwenv_bec4205dd233.aspx"><b>采葛</b></a></p>
<p class="source"><a href="https://www.gushiwen.org/shiwen/default.aspx?cstr=%e5%85%88%e7%a7%a6">先秦</a><span>：</span><a href="/search.aspx?value=%e4%bd%9a%e5%90%8d">佚名</a></p>
<div class="contson" id="contsonbec4205dd233">
彼采葛兮，一日不见，如三月兮！<br />彼采萧兮，一日不见，如三秋兮！<br />彼采艾兮！一日不见，如三岁兮！
